    • Method Detail

      • iterator

        Iterator<EditorCell> iterator​(EditorCell anchor,
                              boolean forward)
        Return iterator over sub-list of child cells contained inside this collection.
        Parameters:
        anchor - first cell, returned by this iterator will be next/prev sibling of this anchor cell depending on the forward parameter
        forward - parameter specifying direction of the iteration. If true then the direction will be from the beginning of this collection to the end of it.
        Returns:
        iterator over child cells
